erdana&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/=\r\nDIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV align=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#000000 size=3D2 face=3DVerdana&gt;(1) On=\r\ne need not pursue siddhis. Siddhis are not a measure of one&#39;s spiritual pro=\r\ngress and neither necessary nor sufficient for liberation.&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DI=\r\nV align=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#000000 size=3D2 face=3DVerdana&gt;(2) It is unwi=\r\nse to pass judgments on yogis like Vivekananda. Ramakrishna never tolerated=\r\n anyone speaking anything slightly critical of Vivekananda as he regarded V=\r\nivekananda as Narayana himself. Why not give him the benefit of doubt and d=\r\nirect your critical faculty and discrimination at somebody/something else? =\r\nNot because it is offensive, but because you cannot be sure!&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;=\r\nDIV align=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#000000 size=3D2 face=3DVerdana&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/FONT=\r\n&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV align=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#000000 size=3D2 face=3DVerdana&gt;Bes=\r\nt regards,&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV align=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#000000 size=3D2 fa=\r\nce=3DVerdana&gt;Narasimha&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV align=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#000000=\r\n size=3D2 face=3DVerdana&gt;--------------------------------------------------=\r\n-----------------&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV align=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#000000 size=\r\n=3D2 face=3DVerdana&gt;&nbsp; Free Jyotish Software, Free Jyotish Lessons, Jyo=\r\ntish Writings,&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV align=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#000000 size=3D=\r\n2 face=3DVerdana&gt;&quot;Do It Yourself&quot; ritual manuals for short Homam and Pitri =\r\nTarpana:&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV align=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#000000 size=3D2 face=\r\n=3DVerdana&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbs=\r\np;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; http://www.VedicAstrologer.org&lt;/FONT=\r\n&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV align=3Dleft&gt;&lt;FO